                <h1>Set 'remodel.jpg' as Your Worksheet Background</h1>
                <p>To insert the picture file 'remodel.jpg' as the worksheet background, start by opening your document. Navigate to the 'Page Layout' tab and select 'Background.' Choose 'Picture' and upload 'remodel.jpg' from your files. Adjust the placement and size as necessary, ensuring a visually appealing and cohesive design for your worksheet.</p>
